{"data":[{"courseName":"CFA L1 基础课（体验课）","courseId":"8a2a5fa451c0c3ad0151c2950ccf0080","subjectId":"8a22ecb5527d453f01527d4b0e500001","subjectName":"CFA Level I","categoryId":"ff80808149cc09f70149f3e7b9534654","categoryName":"CFA","chapterNum":"5","taskNum":"20","taskTotal":"20","teacherName":"CFA明星讲师团","teacherImage":"/upload/201412/e5b55ad1a15448d5bf5f5d1d3ae8f59a.png","teacherHonor":"","teacherId":"ff8080814a04df96014a3d0b71f904df","teacherCertificate":null,"teacherCourseIds":null,"teacherIntroduce":"","teacherSubject":null,"teacherTeachingStyle":null,"courseBackgroundImage":"/upload/201712/27070a062d60498ca280b8fc64fa77ea.jpg","createTime":"1450668526","lastModifyTime":"1513826419","effectiveDay":"270","versionId":"8a2a5fa451c0c3ad0151c2950ccf0080","courseModuleType":"KNOWLEDGE_MODULE","courseModel":"[]","hits":"134","intro":"<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:21pt;\">\r\n\t1. 授课老师程老师寄语：\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t各位同学：\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t大家好！\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t感谢大家选择财萃网网课，欢迎大家和我一起来学习<b>CFA L1</b>这门课，让我们共同努力 ，争取顺利通过这门考试。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<b></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:21pt;\">\r\n\t2. 网络课程结构\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t网络课程按照科目设置，每个科目下设：<br />\r\n前导课：用最通俗的话语介绍本科目的基本概念和基础理论，属于入门级。<br />\r\n基础课：按照CFA考纲详细讲解每个知识点，并配备相应习题，力求全面掌握给个考试要点。<br />\r\n串讲课：针对重点和难点进行深入讲解，以点带面。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:21pt;\">\r\n\t3. L1网络课程内容\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:21pt;\">\r\n\t1) 职业道德\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:21pt;\">\r\n\t2) 定量分析\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:21pt;\">\r\n\t3) 经济学\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:21pt;\">\r\n\t4) 财务报表分析\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:21pt;\">\r\n\t5) 公司理财\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:21pt;\">\r\n\t6) 固定收益\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:21pt;\">\r\n\t7) 权益投资\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:21pt;\">\r\n\t8) 组合管理\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:21pt;\">\r\n\t9) 其它类投资\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:21pt;\">\r\n\t10) 衍生品\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:21pt;\">\r\n\t11) 全球考试形式及内容\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:21pt;\">\r\n\t4. 全球考试形式及内容\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t一级是比较基础的，但是教材是全英文，包含十门课程，并且考题都是“三选一”的单选题，上午120道，下午120道。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\tCFA考试分别为一级是每年6月份和12月份的第一个周六。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t考试时间是上午从9点到12点，下午是从2点到5点，共计6个小时，中间一个小时的吃饭及休息时间。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:21pt;\">\r\n\t5.备考方法：\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t一级大概有700多个大的知识点，2000多小知识点，知识体系非常庞杂。其实英语要求不高，只要有良好的阅读理解能力就好，另外就是数学方面也不是很难，主要内容会涉及到概率统计这方面的。大家在复习的时候可以以kaplan CFA Notes 为主要复习资料，认真掌握每一个知识点即可。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br />\r\n</div>","isEssence":"0","isRecommend":"0","marketPrice":"1000.00000","price":"1000.00000","score":"0","tag":"","title":"CFA L1 基础课（体验课）","courseCategoryId":"8a22ecb5527d453f01527d4b0e500001","firstVideo":"92A2B1E8F03CCA799C33DC5901307461","handoutType":"none","coursePointState":null,"metaDescription":"感谢大家选择财萃网网课，欢迎大家和我一起来学习CFA L1这门课，让我们共同努力 ，争取顺利通过这门考试。","metaKeywords":"CFA L1 基础课（体验课）","metaTitle":"CFA L1 基础课（体验课）-财萃网","courseState":"publish","courseType":"2","handoutFilePath":"","taskCount":"20","teachingType":"onlinecourse","knowledgePointId":"","knowledgeNodeId":"","courseSource":"zhongbo","subjectIndex":"50","categoryIndex":"20","courseIndex":"1","aim":"<span>CFA一级课程共有10门课，其中每门课的平均备考时间30天-60天较好，每天